Ebbro 44574 Nissan Skyline GT-R (R32) 1994 JGTC Series 3rd Place S. Yamaji/S. Sodeyama

Purchased: 2015
Manufacturer page: http://www.ebbro.jp/SHOP/44574.html

1994 was the first full season of the JGTC series. Seiichi Sodeyama & Shin'ichi Yamaji drove this colorful R32 for Racing Team Nakaharu to 3rd place overall. Their best result was 2nd place in the first race of the season at Fuji.
